data.description: ***Offer Deadline Tuesday, 11/28 at 5pm. *** Discover the charm of 15706 Henrietta Dr., a peaceful retreat located in the serene, no-HOA neighborhood of Treeview Estates. This home seamlessly blends comfort with a touch of elegance and is perfectly positioned for those seeking a quiet lifestyle with the convenience of nearby city life with MGM National Harbor and DC just 20 minutes away. The exterior features a warm combination of brick and vinyl siding, complemented by an inviting landscaped yard and a two-car garage. Out back, a spacious deck overlooks a secluded lawn, creating an ideal backdrop for gatherings or quiet evenings.   Enter into a warm and inviting open floor plan, where a stylish living area meets you with elegant columns and a formal dining space. The cozy family room, complete with skylights and vaulted ceilings, centers around a fireplace, seamlessly leading into a modern kitchen featuring a central island and dual ovens. This home includes 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, offering plenty of living space. The highlight is the spacious master suite, which features a sitting area, walk-in closet, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom equipped with a soaking tub, standalone shower, and dual sinks.  The lower level adds approximately 2,500 square feet of living space, bringing the total area of this property to over 5,000 square feet. Discover the expansive, finished basement that includes a cozy second fireplace and direct walkout access to the yard. This space is perfect for customization, with extra rooms and a full bath that are just waiting for your finishing touches. Be sure to take a look at the floor plan to see all it has to offer. Situated in the desirable Treeview Estates, this home is a rare find, providing the perfect blend of spaciousness and privacy. Don’t miss out on the chance to make this inviting residence your own.
